EventML is an interface to the Logic of Events aiming at easing the
specification of concurrent systems' behavior.  It has an ML-like
syntax and is implemented in SML.

The list of people involved in this project is as follows:

  - Mark Bickford
  - Robert L. Constable
  - Richard Eaton
  - David Guaspari
  - Christoph Kreitz
  - Vincent Rahli
